title: Schwabing Affairs
description:
Those cats at Diggler never rest! This is the second fab installment in their "Affairs" series - and what a corker it is!

Taking it&#039;s title from the Schwabing district of Munich (that in the late 60&#039;s belonged to the beatniks, the existentialists and the other hip young things - the &#039;long term students&#039;), Schwabing Affairs is a compilation of groovy and easy tunes taken from the soundtracks of the movies being produced there in the 60&#039;s and 70&#039;s.

There&#039;s tracks from movies such as Engelchen Macht Weiter Hoppe, Hoppe Reiter (Up The Establishment!), Der Kerl Liebt Mich und Das Soil ich Glauben?, MÃƒÂ¤dchen, MÃƒÂ¤dchen (Girls, Girls), Bengelchen Liebt Kreuz und Quer (24-Hour Lover), Jet Generation (How Girls Love Men of Today) and more.

Check Track 11 (Leave This Lesbian World) for the crazy backward-beat thing going on - brilliant!
